name: Strange Evidence
overview: Worldwide, 300 million surveillance cameras are watching us, on our streets, at work, and in our homes. At times, they capture images that don't seem to follow the normal laws of physics. A new Science Channel series investigates mysteries caught on tape and uncovers the science behind some of the most bizarre occurrences ever recorded. With a team of experts analyzing footage that seems to defy explanation, including levitating cars on a freeway, a statue that appears to move on its own, and a spontaneous burst of flames.

episodes.name: Curse of Osiris
episodes.overview: A camera captures a person inexplicably bursting into flames. An ancient statue at a museum appears to come to life at night. An alien-like creature is filmed in the sewers. Eerie lights caught on camera may explain a mysterious death.

episodes.name: Attack of the Fire Devil
episodes.overview: A man is recorded surviving two lightning strikes in moments. Cameras spot strange lights in the Norway sky, turning a remote area into a UFO hot spot. A bizarre glowing object is caught on tape at a museum, and some wonder if it's an alien artifact.

episodes.name: Chasing Bigfoot
episodes.overview: An eerie creature is recorded stalking a Georgia forest, and some believe it's Bigfoot. Terrifying explosions rock the streets of Manhattan. Cameras record a mysterious object diving into a deadly volcano, leaving experts stumped.

episodes.name: The Doomsday Swamp
episodes.overview: A high-speed chase ends when the fugitive makes an impossible getaway. A Louisiana swamp devours 100-foot trees, and experts worry a nearby town could be next. Three cars are filmed mysteriously levitating at a busy intersection.

episodes.name: Night of the Chupacabra
episodes.overview: A camera captures footage of a Chupcabra-like beast. On Hawaii's Mauna Kea, cameras record a mysterious explosion that looks like a nuclear bomb detonated in space. Video of spontaneous combustion is taken at a haunted bar.

episodes.name: Monster of the Deep
episodes.overview: Strange footage captures a mystifying monster, baffling marine biologists. Bizarre ghost lights haunt North Carolina mountains for centuries. When a giant explosion is caught on tape in New Mexico, investigators fear the US is under attack.

episodes.name: Jungle Werewolf
episodes.overview: A strange beast is spotted in a remote Brazilian town. A cataclysmic blast sparks fears of nuclear disaster. When a child displays superhuman powers, some fear it's the devil's work.

episodes.name: Lake of the Dead
episodes.overview: Marine scientists discover a gruesome underwater death zone that seems to kill anything that dares to enter. When apocalyptic skies appear during a deadly earthquake in Ecuador, residents fear it's the end of days.

episodes.name: Ghost in the Abyss
episodes.overview: A deep-ocean expedition discovers unnerving evidence of an alien-like monster stirring in the abyss. When a shockwave is caught on tape, investigators wonder if a meteor has hit a city. Something bizarre is happening in a Siberian ice river.

episodes.name: Vampire Down Under
episodes.overview: A strange creature on the site of one of the worst nuclear disasters ever sparks fears of a terrifying genetic mutation. New evidence suggests a legendary predator with a thirst for blood might have come back from the dead.

episodes.name: Freak of the Deep
episodes.overview: Deep sea explorers discover an unknown monster thousands of feet beneath the ocean. Killer fog threatens a town in the American Midwest. A truck spontaneously explodes on a busy freeway.

episodes.name: America's Loch Ness Monster
episodes.overview: A strange creature like the Loch Ness Monster is recorded in America. Experts analyze evidence of a giant scaly egg, and some wonder if it belongs to a dragon. Birds are suddenly vaporized by an invisible death ray.

episodes.name: Curse of the Mayan Treasure
episodes.overview: An explorer searching for treasure at a Mayan sacrificial site is attacked by a mysterious underwater fog. Thousands of fish spontaneously jump to their deaths. Something alien appears over the skies of Lost Angeles.

episodes.name: Gateway to Hell

episodes.name: Return of the Ice Monster
episodes.overview: A giant creature in an armor of ice is spotted in the Alaskan wild, and some suspect it's a deadly mythical monster. A jet has a close encounter with an unknown object. Evidence of a deadly lightning strike invites paranormal explanations.

episodes.name: The Beast That Ate Jaws
episodes.overview: When a shark is eaten by a mysterious predator, experts wonder if a prehistoric monster is to blame. A sinister sight is caught on tape near Russia's Area 51, and the evidence might point to a cover-up.

episodes.overview: Evidence of ghostly apparitions is captured at a Civil War battlefield. When strange blue fires start near Yellowstone, some worry if a supervolcano eruption is imminent. Near the site of the Salem Witch Trials, an eerie spectacle stuns scientists.

episodes.name: The Omen of Blood River
episodes.overview: When a river of blood washes through a city's streets, some witnesses believe it's a warning of doomsday. A strange perfect circle emerges in the clouds about California, and some experts speculate that it's evidence of alien activity.

episodes.name: Wrath of Thor

episodes.name: Curse of the Monster Spider
episodes.overview: When a massive spider's web takes over a park, experts investigate if this monster's trap could capture a human. A tree spurts out thick red blood, and some believe it could be an undiscovered species of carnivorous plant.

episodes.name: Alien Armageddon Conspiracy
episodes.overview: When a terrifying tower of fire is caught on camera, eyewitnesses fear an alien invasion, and using cutting-edge science, experts investigate the threat causing this nightmarish phenomenon—and if a cover-up is hiding the truth.

episodes.name: Stargate in the Jungle

episodes.name: The Devil's Mutant

episodes.overview: When something strange is recorded flying in Mexico, some wonder if it's a witch reputed to kidnap children, others believe it's evidence of a new way to smuggle drugs or top-secret technology; the latest science helps experts investigate the truth.

episodes.name: Alien in the Abyss
